           IF COD3 = "F" GO TO F-CONS.
           PERFORM LEO-ART02.
           MOVE COD-ART02 TO COD-ART01.
           PERFORM LEO-ART01.
           IF COD3 = "F" GO TO F-CONS.
           IF EMP-ART02 > NUM-EMP GO TO F-CONS.
           IF SUC-ART02 > SUC-EMP GO TO F-CONS.
           MOVE NUM-ART02 TO COD-NUM.
           PERFORM LEO-NUM-R.
