           PERFORM CAP-COD1.
           IF ESCAP GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F03 GO TO C-SIGO-A.
           GO TO F-CONS.
       C-SIGO-A2.
           DISPLAY SPACES LINE 14 POSITION 40 SIZE 30.
           IF COD3 = "F" GO TO F-CONS.
           PERFORM LEO-ART02.
           IF EMP-ART02 > NUM-EMP GO TO F-CONS.
           IF SUC-ART02 > SUC-EMP GO TO F-CONS.
           IF NUM-ART02 NOT = COD-NUM
