           PERFORM LEO-MAR-R.
           IF COD3 = "F" GO TO F-CONS.
           IF PRE-V-ART02 = 0 GO TO COSTO-S-A.
           PERFORM DES-MAR.
           PERFORM DES-COD THRU DES-POS.
           IF COD NOT = "A" GO TO C-LEO-A.
           PERFORM MEN-CONF.
           MOVE 3 TO SW3.
           PERFORM CAP-COD1.
           IF F01 PERFORM CARGA-PRE THRU CARGA-FEC-V
